---
title: Wontons, Spring Rolls & Dumplings Hot, crispy, and oh-so-dippable! | 8 Servings
description: These wontons are the perfect combination of spicy and sweet: jalapeño peppers and cream cheese filling are wrapped in a deliciously crispy wonton wrapper. They’re gooey on the inside and crunchy on the outside. And what could be better than gyoza (Japanese-style dumplings) from SUMM?! Why, serving them alongside crispy golden vegetable spring rolls, of course! Filled with minced pork, cabbage, scallions, shiitake mushrooms, and ginger, these dumplings pair perfectly with cabbage, carrot, and mushroom-packed spring rolls. This threesome makes the perfect meal, app, or anytime snack! No matter how you heat them up, these gems are best served with SUMM! (Sauces included!)

